tomatoes
================================================================================
Utility for time boxing using the Pomodoro technique.

Keeps track of your tomatoes, when they were started and whether they succeeded.

All tomatoes are stored in a CSV file for easy data visualization.

Usage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
$ tomatoes start <task_name> # Start a new tomato
$ tomatoes failure           # Report failure (interrupted)
$ tomatoes success           # Report success
$ tomatoes status            # Prints status of  current tomato

